  "keyFeatures": [
    "Data-driven campaign system: missions, targets, vulnerabilities, and narrative live in RON files — no Rust required",
    "Reusable simterm-engine library crate with no UI dependency",
    "Terminal UI powered by ratatui and crossterm",
    "Virtual filesystem for post-exploitation exploration, clues, and objectives",
    "Declarative campaign commands with conditional effects (flags, trace, achievements, mission completion)",
    "Multi-host network missions with pivoting and token-based lateral movement",
    "Synthesized POSIX shell (uname, ps, netstat, env, grep, etc.) from host definitions",
    "Imperfect information model: tool affinity, reliability tiers (Reliable / Unstable), false positives",
    "Offline analysis and reversing puzzles: hash cracking, binary strings/disasm, Base64/XOR encoding",
    "Optional per-mission WAV music with fade-in and looping",
    "Semantic validation via --doctor: dangling refs, unreachable content, bad ranges",
    "Autoplay modes (--autoplay and --autoplay-deterministic) for end-to-end playability testing",
    "Achievement system: engine-level and campaign-defined data-driven achievements"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
